<p sourcefile="V1/Configuration/OSIsoft Adapter for OPC UA security configuration.md" sourcestartlinenumber="45" sourceendlinenumber="45">Windows:</p>
<pre sourcefile="V1/Configuration/OSIsoft Adapter for OPC UA security configuration.md" sourcestartlinenumber="47" sourceendlinenumber="49"><code class="lang-filepath">%programdata%\OSIsoft\Adapters\OpcUa\Certificates\rejected\certs
</code></pre><p sourcefile="V1/Configuration/OSIsoft Adapter for OPC UA security configuration.md" sourcestartlinenumber="51" sourceendlinenumber="51">Linux:</p>
<pre sourcefile="V1/Configuration/OSIsoft Adapter for OPC UA security configuration.md" sourcestartlinenumber="53" sourceendlinenumber="55"><code class="lang-filepath">/usr/share/OSIsoft/Adapters/OpcUa/Certificates/rejected/certs
