<pre sourcefile="V1/Configuration/OSIsoft Adapter for OPC UA security configuration.md" sourcestartlinenumber="67" sourceendlinenumber="69"><code class="lang-filepath">/usr/share/OSIsoft/Adapters/OpcUa/Certificates/trusted/certs
</code></pre><h4 id="certificate-of-the-adapter" sourcefile="V1/Configuration/OSIsoft Adapter for OPC UA security configuration.md" sourcestartlinenumber="71" sourceendlinenumber="71">Certificate of the adapter</h4>
